Description:
    Creates a new AngularJS decorator for a specified service

Example:
    yo angular-feature:decorator serviceName [--coffee]

    This will create (division by component):
        app/scripts/decorators/serviceNameDecorator.js

    or (division by feature):
    	app/src/common/decorators/serviceNameDecorator.js


    yo angular-feature:decorator foo/serviceName [--coffee]

    This will create (division by feature):
        app/src/foo/decorators/serviceNameDecorator.js


    yo angular-feature:decorator foo/bar/serviceName [--coffee]

    This will create (division by feature):
        app/src/foo/bar/decorators/serviceNameDecorator.js